                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span>                        
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="radio">
                    <input id="q1_option2" type="radio" name="question1" value="option2"
                        data-answer="answer" />
                    <label for="q1_option2">
                        Perfect Strangers
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok"></span>
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></span>
                    </label>
                    <p class="answer-explain">
                        Yes. I liked it. I like it a lot. Let's put some more placeholder
